{"tid":861059,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制有得揀　維園阿叔　伍迪希　九西補選　深水埗收集提名","createTime":"2018-10-13T19:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T19:43:01.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"767c049482b65b9da04e1167f3da309c43807e66","tid":861059,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:40:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tmhk.org/2018/10/13/【九西補選】伍迪希深水埗爭取提名-主張23條盡快/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftmhk.org%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B9%9D%E8%A5%BF%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E4%BC%8D%E8%BF%AA%E5%B8%8C%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E6%8F%90%E5%90%8D-%E4%B8%BB%E5%BC%B523%E6%A2%9D%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%2F&d=d5UT30PJ%2BcWmjSrsGt973zACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=ed060874\" target=\"_blank\">https://tmhk.org/2018/10/13/【九西補選】伍迪希深水埗爭取提名-主張23條盡快/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/B6C29B78-4955-4E83-B695-ACE70F2715D7.jpeg?resize=800%2C445&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FB6C29B78-4955-4E83-B695-ACE70F2715D7.jpeg%3Fresize%3D800%252C445%26ssl%3D1&h=2101f14e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【九西補選】伍迪希深水埗爭取提名　主張23條盡快立法<br />\n<br />\n13/10/2018<br />\n<br />\n立法會九龍西補選提名期將於下週一完結，曾參與年初港島區補選的伍迪希是日早上在深水埗收集市民提名。<br />\n<br />\n據伍於社交網絡上表示他現居於深水埗區內的唐樓劏房，希望爭取全面租務管制，保護基層市民的生存空間。他強調自己不是求勝，只希望透過媒體辯論及訪問令社會明白基層市民的生活狀況。<br />\n<br />\n在熱議政策上，他希望《基本法》二十三條能盡快立法，亦認同填海是可以增加土地的最佳方法。<br />\n<br />\n已參選立法會九龍西補選有陳凱欣、馮檢基及李卓人。"},{"pid":"dd32182180806ee05d9a11fc151ff157d678115f","tid":861059,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:43:01.000Z","msg":"支持參選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}